# Local credentials (never commit)
GoogleService-Info.plist
# google-services.json is committed: it's client Firebase config (restricted
# Android API key, shipped in the APK) and EAS Build needs it in the git archive
# for Android FCM. The real secret (FCM v1 service-account key) lives in EAS, not git.

